2008-10-02  Wakaba  <wakaba@suika.fam.cx>

	* schema.cgi: Changed the diff-sync mode to be in UTF-8.
	($no_sync_pattern): |label| added.
	(get_map, set_map): Drop old Data::Dumper .map support.

2008-10-02  Wakaba  <wakaba@suika.fam.cx>

	* schema.cgi: Create copies of maps using Storable, since
	Data::Dumper is the most significant bottleneck of the script.

2008-10-02  Wakaba  <wakaba@suika.fam.cx>

	* schema.cgi: diff-sync mode supported.
	(serialize_prop_hash): Sort certain multivalue properties by their
	values.

